Prerequisites
-------------

 * Migen (https://github.com/m-labs/migen)
 * mkbof (https://github.com/brandonhamilton/rhino/tree/master/borph/tools/borph)
 * Xilinx ISE command line tools
 * Python 3.3

Building
--------

To build all applications:
$ python3 build.py

To build only specified applications:
$ python3 build.py application1 application2

Look in the application output directory for the .bof file
